lor: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;作，通过&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;实施&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;完善&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;和&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;简化的咨询、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;检测、关怀、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;治疗和随访模式&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;提高当地艾滋病预防和治疗应对能力，扩大检测覆盖面和可及性，最大程度&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-space