es&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;已覆盖全国&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;14&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;个省、自治区（直辖市），包括山西&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;、河南、重庆、广西&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;云南&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;、北京、上海、海南、黑龙江、广东、四川&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;、湖南、浙江和天津。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;基于此&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;qu