uot;&gt;服务近11万&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;人次&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;发现&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;艾滋病&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;感染者&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;4,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;711&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;人&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;，总检测阳性率为&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;.41%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;，全年&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;新增&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;治疗&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;和关怀人数27&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;957&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;人。201&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;年3月底&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;AHF&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;项目网络&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;正&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;为超过&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;357位&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;艾滋病&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;病毒感染者和&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;病人提供治疗&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;和关怀服务&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(86, 86, 86); font-family: 华文楷体; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 华文楷体;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;_baidu_bookmark_end_19&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 0px; display: none;&quot;&gt;‍&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;_baidu_bookmark_end_17&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 0px; display: none;&quot;&gt;‍&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;_baidu_bookmark_end_15&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 0px; display: none;&quot;&gt;‍&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;_baidu_bookmark_end_13&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 0px; display: none;&quot;&gt;‍&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;_baidu_bookmark_end_11&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 0px; display: none;&quot;&gt;‍&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;_baidu_bookmark_end_9&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 0px; display: none;&quot;&gt;‍&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;_baidu_bookmark_end_7&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 0px; display: none;&quot;&gt;‍&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;_baidu_bookmark_end_5&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 0px; display: none;&quot;&gt;‍&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;_baidu_bookmark_end_3&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 0px; display: none;&quot;&gt;‍&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;_baidu_bookmark_end_1&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 0px; display: none;&quot;&gt;‍&lt;/span&gt;',1,1498464379,1500347874,0,0),(54,'京津冀大学校园安全套艺术创意作品征集活动进入专家评选阶段！','&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 1em 0px 0pt; text-indent: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;在北京佑安医院感染中心及艾滋病健&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;康&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;基金&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;会&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;（&lt;/span&gt;AHF）的支持下，佑安爱心家园.恬园工作室于2017年上半年举办了京津冀大学校园防艾宣传—&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;《安全套艺术创意作品征集评选活动》&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;。自&lt;/span&gt;2017年4月10日起&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;由医护人员、艾滋病病毒感染者及高校大学生防艾志愿者组建了防艾宣传小组开始在北京、天津、河北保定地区高校进行防艾宣传和动员高校学生参与到艺术创作活动中&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 1em 0px 0pt; text-indent: 36pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;北京首都医科大学、中国人民大学、北京交通运输学院、北京建筑大学、首都经贸大学、首都工商大学、首都医科大学燕京护理学院、华北电力大学（河北保定校区）、天津医科大学、天津美术学院、天津外国语大学、天津中德应用技术大学、天津商业大学等高&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 楷体;&quot;&gt;校&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-family: 楷体; font-size: 14pt; mso-spacerun: &amp;quot;yes&amp;quot;; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-famil